99
Your application provides data transformation servies. Files containing data to be transformed are first upload to Amazon S3 and then transformed by a fleet of spot EC2 instance. Files submitted by your premium cunstomers must be transformed with the highest priority. How should you implement such a system?
Use tow SQS queues, one for high priority messages, the other for default priority. Transformation instances first poll the high priority queue; if there is no message, they poll the default priority queue

